<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="Leonor Bravo Fried — Psicóloga Clínica en Santiago. Terapia individual para adultos. Atención presencial en Providencia y online.">
<title>Leonor Bravo · Psicóloga Clínica · Santiago</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --sage: #7A8C7A;
    --sage-light: #B8C9B3;
    --sage-pale: #EDF1EC;
    --terracota: #C4785A;
    --terracota-light: #E8B49A;
    --cream: #FAF7F2;
    --ink: #2C2C27;
    --ink-mid: #5C5C52;
    --ink-muted: #9E9E90;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(122, 140, 122, 0.15);
    padding: 0 48px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .nav-logo span {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--terracota); }

  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--terracota) !important;
    color: var(--white) !important;
    padding: 8px 20px !important;
    border-radius: 32px !important;
    font-weight: 500 !important;
    transition: background 0.2s !important;
  }

  .nav-cta:hover { background: #B56A4E !important; }

  .nav-toggle {
    display: none;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 4px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 64px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    padding: 80px 48px 80px 72px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
  }

  .hero-heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(44px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracota);
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    max-width: 440px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--terracota);
    color: var(--white);
    border: none;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: #B56A4E; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .btn-ghost {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-ghost::after { content: '→'; transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--sage); }
  .btn-ghost:hover::after { transform: translateX(3px); }

  /* ── HERO VISUAL ── */
  .hero-visual {
    height: 100vh;
    background: var(--sage-pale);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-photo-frame {
    width: 100%;
    height: 85%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--sage-pale) 0%, #D4DFD1 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Reemplaza este div con <img src="foto-leonor.jpg"> */
  .hero-photo-placeholder {
    width: 260px;
    height: 340px;
    border-radius: 130px 130px 20px 20px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
    opacity: 0.5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 48px;
    left: -32px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44, 44, 39, 0.12);
    max-width: 200px;
  }

  .hero-badge-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--terracota);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-badge-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    margin-top: 4px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .hero-deco-dot {
    position: absolute;
    top: 48px;
    right: 48px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--terracota-light);
    opacity: 0.35;
  }

  .hero-deco-ring {
    position: absolute;
    top: 32px;
    right: 32px;
    width: 112px;
    height: 112px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--terracota-light);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS BASE ── */
  .section-pad {
    padding: 96px 72px;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .section-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 20px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
  }

  .section-eyebrow.center { justify-content: center; }
  .section-eyebrow.center::before { display: none; }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracota);
  }

  .section-body {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* ── SOBRE MÍ ── */
  .sobre-mi-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .credenciales {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .credencial {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .credencial-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--terracota);
    margin-top: 7px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .credencial-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .credencial-text strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .foto-sobre-mi {
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: var(--sage-pale);
    border-radius: 8px 80px 8px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--sage-light);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .foto-sobre-mi img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ── ESPECIALIDADES ── */
  .especialidades-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(122, 140, 122, 0.12);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(44, 44, 39, 0.08);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--sage-pale);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .card-icon svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    stroke: var(--sage);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.5;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .card-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── PROCESO ── */
  .proceso-bg {
    background: var(--ink);
  }

  .proceso-bg .section-eyebrow { color: var(--sage-light); }
  .proceso-bg .section-eyebrow::before { background: var(--sage); }
  .proceso-bg .section-heading { color: var(--white); }
  .proceso-bg .section-body { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

  .proceso-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 64px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .step {
    padding: 36px 28px;
    background: var(--ink);
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .step:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }

  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .step-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.42);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── TESTIMONIOS ── */
  .testimonios-bg { background: var(--sage-pale); }

  .testimonios-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .testimonio {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .testimonio-quote {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .testimonio-author {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
  }

  /* ── AGENDA ── */
  .agenda-bg {
    background: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .agenda-bg .section-heading { margin: 0 auto 20px; }
  .agenda-bg .section-body { margin: 0 auto 40px; }

  .agenda-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--terracota);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--terracota);
    padding: 13px 32px;
    border-radius: 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--terracota); color: var(--white); }

  .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(122, 140, 122, 0.15);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
  }

  .contact-item::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sage-light);
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 32px 72px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  }

  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 0 24px; }

    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .nav-toggle { display: block; }

    .nav-links.open {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: fixed;
      top: 64px; left: 0; right: 0;
      background: var(--cream);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(122,140,122,0.15);
      padding: 24px;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .hero-content {
      padding: 60px 24px 40px;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      height: 60vw;
      min-height: 320px;
    }

    .hero-badge { left: 16px; }

    .sobre-mi-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .foto-sobre-mi { max-height: 320px; }

    .especialidades-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }

    .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }

    .proceso-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }

    .testimonios-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

    .section-pad { padding: 64px 24px; }

    footer { padding: 28px 24px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .proceso-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ── ACCESIBILIDAD ── */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    *, *::before, *::after { transition: none !important; animation: none !important; }
  }

  :focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--terracota);
    outline-offset: 3px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAV ── -->
<nav aria-label="Navegación principal">
  <a href="#inicio" class="nav-logo" aria-label="Ir al inicio">
    Leonor Bravo
    <span>Psicóloga Clínica</span>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links" id="nav-menu" role="list">
    <li><a href="#sobre-mi">Sobre mí</a></li>
    <li><a href="#especialidades">Especialidades</a></li>
    <li><a href="#proceso">El proceso</a></li>
    <li><a href="#agenda" class="nav-cta">Agendar sesión</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-toggle" id="nav-toggle" aria-label="Abrir menú" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="nav-menu">
    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round">
      <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="19" y2="6"/>
      <line x1="3" y1="11" x2="19" y2="11"/>
      <line x1="3" y1="16" x2="19" y2="16"/>
    </svg>
  </button>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section id="inicio" class="hero" aria-label="Inicio">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow" aria-hidden="true">Psicología clínica · Santiago</div>
    <h1 class="hero-heading">
      Un espacio para<br>
      <em>encontrarte</em><br>
      contigo mismo
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-body">
      Acompañamiento psicológico para adultos que buscan comprender sus patrones, 
      sanar lo que duele y construir una vida con más sentido.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#agenda" class="btn-primary">Reservar primera sesión</a>
      <a href="#sobre-mi" class="btn-ghost">Conocer más</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="hero-photo-frame">
      <!-- Reemplaza este div por: <img src="img/foto-leonor.jpg" alt="Leonor Bravo, psicóloga"> -->
      <div class="hero-photo-placeholder"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-deco-dot"></div>
    <div class="hero-deco-ring"></div>
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <div class="hero-badge-num">+12</div>
      <div class="hero-badge-text">años acompañando procesos de cambio</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── SOBRE MÍ ── -->
<section id="sobre-mi" class="section-pad" style="background: var(--white);">
  <div class="sobre-mi-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Sobre mí</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Creo en el <em>cambio real</em>,<br>el que se construye desde adentro</h2>
      <p class="section-body">
        Soy Leonor Bravo, psicóloga clínica con especialización en psicoterapia cognitivo-conductual 
        y enfoque humanista. Mi trabajo está centrado en crear un espacio seguro donde puedas explorar 
        tu historia, entender tus respuestas y decidir cómo quieres vivir.
      </p>

      <div class="credenciales">
        <div class="credencial">
          <div class="credencial-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="credencial-text">
            <strong>Psicóloga clínica — [Universidad]</strong>
            Licenciatura con mención en psicología clínica y de la salud
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="credencial">
          <div class="credencial-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="credencial-text">
            <strong>Especialización en terapia cognitivo-conductual</strong>
            Formación continua en TCC, ACT y terapia de esquemas
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="credencial">
          <div class="credencial-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="credencial-text">
            <strong>Atención presencial y online</strong>
            Providencia, Santiago · sesiones en español
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="foto-sobre-mi">
      <!-- Reemplaza por: <img src="img/foto-sobre-mi.jpg" alt="Leonor Bravo en consulta"> -->
      <span style="color: var(--sage-light); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">[foto profesional]</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── ESPECIALIDADES ── -->
<section id="especialidades" class="section-pad" style="background: var(--cream);">
  <div class="especialidades-intro">
    <div>
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Especialidades</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Áreas en las que <em>trabajo</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-body" style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 20px;">
      Cada proceso es único. Adapto el enfoque terapéutico a lo que tú necesitas, no al revés.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="cards-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="card-title">Ansiedad y estrés</h3>
      <p class="card-body">Herramientas concretas para regular la angustia y romper los ciclos que te mantienen atrapado.</p>
    </article>

